<h1 id="fremium-services">Fremium Services</h1>

<p>Companies like <a href="https://www.mapbox.com/mapbox-studio/">mapbox</a> and google provide some geospatial services that are “free” to a point.  For example, <a href="https://code.earthengine.google.com/">Google earth engine</a> provides its cloud based computational capabilities to non-commercial users free of charge.</p>

